See Measles update (65): Africa, USA 20181025.6112636: The MMR vaccine clinics are in response to 15 confirmed cases to date in Rockland, said Rockland County Executive Ed Day and County Health Commissioner Dr Patricia Schnabel Ruppert. Now with 46 cases, officials are offering shots for babies as young as 6 months, because measles is more dangerous for little children.]

